Introduction

WEi is a six-member boy group under OUI Entertainment. They made their official debut in October 2020 with the mini-album "Identity: First Sight."

The group comprises former RAINZ member Jang Daehyeon, former JBJ member Kim Donghan, former 1THE9 members Yoo Yongha and Kim Junseo, former X1 member Kim Yohan, and former YG Treasure Box participant Kang Seokhwa. All members have previously participated in reality shows such as Produce 101 Season 2, Under Nineteen, Produce X 101, and YG TREASURE BOX.
